msgid ""
"Ziram is a trusted pesticide utilized for its broad-spectrum defense against "
"fungi and pests. This protective solution shields plants by inhibiting "
"disease and infestation, contributing to improved crop yield and overall "
"plant health."
msgstr ""
"Ziram ist ein bewährtes Pestizid, das wegen seines breiten Wirkungsspektrums "
